headline: Agoda and Macao Government Tourism Office Join Forces to Showcase Macao's Unique Charms
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has partnered with Macao Government Tourism Office (MGTO) to showcase the Special Administrative Region as a must-visit destination for international travelers. Macao, celebrated as a 'Culture City of East Asia 2025,' is well placed to attract global travelers with its luxury accommodation, distinctive cultural experiences and world-class entertainment.
